description: Both these girls are skilled and have been doing excellent this season. Daisy won this year's Rookie Cup Championship. That doesn't mean much to Cheyenne. The Wrangler is here to kick ass and humiliate all rookies by beating the best one on the roster. Winner Tramples loser with dirty boots, makes her worship her ass and then fists her.
title: Rookie Cup Champion takes on Wrangler Team Captain
